column5: Take a deep breath, read the rules, be more tolerant of others opinions, try to be a little less crass and offensive, and try not to forget that we're all here to talk about fishing.  Here's a video to get us back on page... http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0yY3NniApsc
I can't believe I missed that discussion... I was too busy putting the new laws to use and breaking some of the outdated ones!!!
And now back to work. Good laughs. BTW, silly season approaches, hopefully nobody gets too pissy and punchy this year.
